usters have angular momentum parameters\n$\\lambda_R\\lesssim 0.5$ and show Gauss-Hermite coefficients $h_3$ that are\nanti-correlated with the velocity, indicating asymmetric line-of-sight velocity\ndistributions as a signature of a dissipative formation process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2020 18:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 18:19:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-02"}
