mized to run\nin time n^{O(1)} and use O(log n) bits of space.\n  Our results use a combination of ideas from the theory of kernelization,\ndistributed algorithms and randomized algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2020 21:08:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2021 07:21:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-23"}
