. An alternative exact analytic solution in the contact limit is\nobtained, for which the torque is zero and the far-field flow is one of uniform\nrotation; in a rotating frame of reference in which the fluid at infinity is at\nrest, the relative flow in this case is identified as a `radial quadrupole'.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2020 22:01:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-12"}
