ch are given by the separation\nand full width at half maximum of the individual Gaussians. Finally, we compare\nour results from two layer stacks with data from X-ray fluorescence\nspectroscopy, which is a standard method for measuring ultra thin films.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 11:11:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Nov 2020 15:45:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
