 real-space distribution of the quasirandom structures using\ndifferent numerical seeds, simulating variations in a self-assembly method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 15:27:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 19:03:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
